<h1 class="mb-4 cyan-text page-title">My most important projects</h1>

<div class="flex content-line">
    <div class="flex-vert mw-60">
        <div class="flex">
            <img class="image" src="~/images/projects/woa/logo2.png" width="40px" height="40px" />
            <h4><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.WorldofAgriculture.WorldofAgriculture" target="_blank" class="cyan-text">World of Agriculture</a></h4>
        </div>

        <p>My first complete game was made towards the end of university in connection with my thesis. It was made with the Unity engine, It was a long project because there were a lot of new things but I also learned a lot. W.o.A is a 2D agricultural manager game published on Android as a free game. The graphics and images were made by me, mainly to test my skills in this department as well.</p>
