            <h4><a href="https://github.com/szuhi27/BattleShips" target="_blank" class="cyan-text">BattleShips</a></h4>
            <p>A Windows Forms application, my first bigger C# project. It was for a university class which was held by NI. My programming skills were not so good at the time, but I got praise for my UI design. This was the first game where I had to implement some kind of computer enemy it was a simple one but I think the gameplay is good.</p>
